        <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Eligibility & Precautions</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <h3 class="mb-3">Donor Eligibility Requirements</h3>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i><strong>Age:</strong> You must be between 18 and 65 years old.</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i><strong>Weight:</strong> You must weigh at least 50 kg (110 lbs).</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i><strong>Health:</strong> You must be in good general health and feeling well.</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i><strong>Lifestyle:</strong> Wait 6 months after getting a tattoo or piercing.</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-times-circle text-danger me-2"></i><strong>Cannot Donate if:</strong> You have a cold, flu, or other infection.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <h3 class="mb-3">Donation Day Precautions</h3>
                        <h5 class="text-danger">Before Your Donation</h5>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled mb-3">
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-utensils text-primary me-2"></i>Eat an iron-rich meal a few hours before.</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-tint text-primary me-2"></i>Drink plenty of water (an extra 500ml).</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-id-card text-primary me-2"></i>Bring a valid photo ID.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <h5 class="text-danger">After Your Donation</h5>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-cookie-bite text-primary me-2"></i>Rest and enjoy the provided snack and drink.</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-ban text-primary me-2"></i>Avoid heavy lifting or strenuous exercise for the rest of the day.</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-water text-primary me-2"></i>Continue to hydrate well.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

